ABOUT WUDUP SERIES
Wudup is a series created by Artkelso (Ritchie Ned Hansel) presenting a repetition of his trademark character Mr. Chicken Bird. Here the series will be featured with guest stars that will appear on the right side of the artboards, it can be anything that the creator thinks is interesting he sees or interacts with within the day the artwork was created. Enjoy and don't have a good day, HAVE A GREAT DAY!
